text: Andreyevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Kayrakovsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 43 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 23 km from Mishkino, 5 km from Kayrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Andreyevka, Mishkinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
